trinsic Frenet-Serret\nformulae, and the intrinsic Jacobi methods presented here. The relationship of\nGaussian beams to Riemannian curvature is explained with an overview of the\nmodern covariant geometric methods that provide a general framework for\napplication to other special cases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 6 Apr 2013 19:38:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 18 Apr 2014 15:07:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-12"}
