 at\nshorter distances reveal characteristic features that result from the fact that\nthe vdW-DF method is an electron-based (as opposed to atom-based) description.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 6 Apr 2013 21:25:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-04-09"}
